parameters:
Finally, it seems like I can start retaining my
memories.

Ah, what a shame. I was able to remember without a
kiss.

What's wrong, feeling lonely? If you want, we can
do it.

Y-You're obviously lying! It's creepy, don't come
near me.

But more importantly... Jackson was supposed to be
the culprit.
I confirmed it properly in the previous loop.
However, the ritual has already begun.
I think... Jackson might not be the culprit.

There was someone who was trying to perform the
ritual, you know.

That magic circle was supposed to have been
confiscated by the student council.

(It's hard to believe that the student council is
behind this...)

(No, I don't know much about the student council.
Especially that vice president, they're quite
mysterious.)

Hey, I'm here too. Don't get lost in your thoughts
alone.

Let's investigate the student council next. It's
strange that they don't have a president.

I wonder if getting close to Hiyo, a student
council member in the same class, is the fastest
way.
When did we come to a conclusion?

(Anyway, let's make sure to stay away from the
Magic Research Club.)

(I don't know her well to begin with, so maybe
it's worth trying to get closer in reverse.)

(The one who did the worst thing to Amelia in the
beginning was Professor Hoffman.)

Alright, let's do our best. First, it's time for
class.
I hope I can become friends with Hiyo.
particle play warp_red_cp player def above
